{"tid":428043,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"COOL牙問題一問","createTime":"2017-10-07T18:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T14:28:22.000Z","uid":126178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"995a9ceeb30994b8e7b67e3d6e3673a142066111","tid":428043,"uid":126178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T18:40:36.000Z","msg":"請問有無兔仔牙/哨牙既過來人 COOL完牙？<br />\n<br />\n因為我本身係兔仔牙 兩隻門牙哨左出黎 <br />\n<br />\nCOOL左兩年幾未得都算喇<br />\n<br />\n但兩隻門牙本身糖痴豆黎 無喇喇近一年COOL到出左條牙縫 仲愈來愈大條LA <br />\n<br />\n因為仲有半個月先覆診 但最近好在意佢<br />\n<br />\n有無好心人解答下我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39a86e1eafa98b0817a68236fd816fc1462a101","tid":428043,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T19:00:14.000Z","msg":"打去問下牙醫點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 以前都係哨牙"},{"pid":"38e8c987a4120de943b527719bab791515c71066","tid":428043,"uid":60864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"我又係兩隻門牙哨出嚟走去箍牙<br />\n箍嗰陣有一排都係兩隻門牙中間會有個隙<br />\n因為啲牙移緊位去中線，要慢慢拉<br />\n係有啲肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你當參考好啦<br />\n你牙醫一定最清楚 你問下佢啦<br />\n擔心就去問 你幫襯佢 你有權知道自己箍牙嘅狀況"}]}